8. Prop Runtime Contract (Implementation Detail)
8.1. Event order on bullet hit:
Apply crit -> apply mark or vulnerability multiplier -> apply direct-hit damage -> process on-hit status (bleed, DoT, chill) -> process on-kill effects (explosion, shrapnel) if the target died.

8.2. Event order on player damage:
Base shield -> temporary shield -> carapace reserve -> HP.
Then trigger on-shield-damaged effects (Retaliation Core / Mirror Shell).
Then trigger on-HP-threshold effects (Guardian Charm).

