9. Balance Verification Checklist
9.1. Single-path stress test:
Run 20-wave tests with pure Ballistic, Shield, Economy, and Status builds.
Target: no path should exceed 1.35x the average win rate of the comparison set.

9.2. Hybrid-path test:
Test 2+2 split builds (e.g., Ballistic + Shield, Economy + Status).
Target: hybrids should have a smoother power curve but a lower peak than the best specialized build.

9.3. Boss test:
Ensure no single prop can kill a mid-game boss in <8s without strong synergy.
